### Prerequisite
# Set `userId` and `providerApiToken` in `queries/http-client.private.env.json`

### Store NanoGPT Credential
POST {{adminApiBaseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/provider-credentials
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{userId}}",
  "providerId": "nanogpt",
  "label": "primary",
  "apiToken": "{{providerApiToken}}"
}
